CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, February 28, 1938, pg. unknown, reads: "The Synchronettes (lower right) composed of non-natives of Pittsburgh is one of the towns most fashionable clubs. They are Geraldine Henry, Ethel Harris, Catherine Watkins, Ruth King, Addie Garvin, Winnie Nickens, Winnie Houston, Stina Mae Fish, Sydney Smith, Catherine Smith, and Bessie Cornelius. (Pgh. photos by Charles 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Synchronettes Club members, including Geraldine Henry, Ethel Harris, Catherine Watkins, Ruth King, Addie Garvin, Winnie Nickens, Winnie Houston, Stina Mae Fish, Sydney Smith, Catherine Smith, and Bessie Cornelius posed in Loendi Club
